#: ../../source/api_reference/playback.rst:16
#: 6cd583aa601c47d8a0e926b2d20f3888
msgid ""
"**FmodChannelControl** 封装 FMOD::ChannelControl 的共享能力，为 :ref:`FmodChannel<FmodChannel>` 和 :ref:`FmodChannelGroup<FmodChannelGroup>` 提供播放控制、音量、3D 空间化、声像矩阵、滤波、DSP 链和样本精确调度等功能。"
msgstr ""
"**FmodChannelControl** wraps the shared FMOD::ChannelControl features used by :ref:`FmodChannel<FmodChannel>` and :ref:`FmodChannelGroup<FmodChannelGroup>`, including playback control, volume, 3D spatialization, pan and mix matrices, filtering, DSP chains, and sample-accurate scheduling."

